            "AltText": "Monochrome photograph. Backed by a small band with simple instruments, six women in work shirts and dusty pants perform outdoors for a tightly-packed crowd. Nearby, a portrait of Mao Zedong hangs under banners that read “serving for the people”, “modesty helps one to move forward” and “conceit makes one fall behind”.",
            "AltTextTC": "黑白照片中，六個女人身穿工作服和沾滿塵埃的長褲，在擠擁的群眾面前進行戶外表演，身後的小型樂隊正演奏簡單樂器。附近掛着一幅毛澤東肖像，肖像上面的橫額寫着「為人民服務」，兩旁的直幅分別寫着「虛心使人進步」和「驕傲使人落後」。",
